summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City Light Department, granting an easement for two communication cabinets and underground communication cables and accepting releases of easement for one cabinet and underground communication cables upon, under, and across portions of the City of Seattle's PNT Transmission Line Right of Way within Lots 13 and 15, Block 2, North Park Addition to the City of Seattle, King County, Washington (P.M. \#260431-2-301).
